trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.

trans-unit.target: Tentativa de utilizar estas classes de dentro de um dos seguintes tipos de aplicação poderá produzir problemas inesperados, tal como o seu serviço exceções de desempenho e o tempo de execução.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.

trans-unit.target: Versões de todos os recursos utilizados pelo <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar Dispose quando tiver terminado de utilizando <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose deixa o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>num Estado não utilizável.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar Dispose, tem de libertar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>para que o recoletor de lixo pode reclame a memória que a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>foi occupying.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [recursos não geridos limpeza](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método eliminar](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada eliminar antes de libertar a última referência <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the `Finalize` method of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está a utilizar não são libertados até que as chamadas de recoletor de lixo a `Finalize` método o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>objeto.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs"></xref> object and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Liberta os recursos não geridos que são utilizados pelo <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs"> </xref> objeto e, opcionalmente, liberta os recursos geridos.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Este método é denominado <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`invoca protegida `Dispose(Boolean)` método com o parâmetro booleano sem nome definido como `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>invoca `Dispose` com o parâmetro definido como `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando é o parâmetro booleano `true`, este método versões todos os recursos que são detidos por quaisquer objetos geridos que este <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>referências.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertiesChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método invoca o `Dispose()` método de cada objeto referenciado.
